[package]
name = "gtfs-structures"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Tristram Gr√§bener <tristramg@gmail.com>", "Antoine Desbordes <antoine.desbordes@gmail.com>"]
description = "Read GTFS (public transit timetables) files"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/rust-transit/gtfs-structure"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
bytes = "1"
chrono = "0.4"
csv = "1.1"
derivative = "2.1"
itertools = "0.10"
rgb = "0.8"
serde_derive = "1.0"
sha2 = "0.10"
thiserror = "1"
zip = "0.5"

[dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11"
features = ["blocking"]
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["rc"]

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0"

[features]
default = ["read-url"]
read-url = ["reqwest", "futures"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "gtfs_structures"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2018"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
